### Encounter Endpoints Testing
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get all encounters (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters?page=0&size=20&sortBy=date&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get upcoming encounters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get encounter by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create a new encounter (with JSON data only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="encounter"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Community Prayer Meeting",
  "description": "Join us for a special prayer meeting to seek God's guidance and blessings for our community.",
  "date": "2025-11-20T18:00:00",
  "location": "Prayer Room"
}
--boundary--

### 5. Create a new encounter (with image)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="encounter"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bible Study Session",
  "description": "Weekly Bible study focusing on the Book of Romans. All are welcome!",
  "date": "2025-11-25T19:00:00",
  "location": "Fellowship Hall"
}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="encounter.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/image.jpg
--boundary--

### 6. Update an encounter
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="encounter"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Community Prayer Meeting",
  "description": "Updated description for the prayer meeting.",
  "date": "2025-11-21T18:00:00",
  "location": "Main Sanctuary"
}
--boundary--

### 7. Delete an encounter
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get my encounters (encounters organized by current user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/my-encounters?page=0&size=20&sortBy=date&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Search encounters by title or location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/search?query=prayer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Search encounters by location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/encounters/search?query=hall
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
